Native vs Web
=============

Discuss the advantages and disadvantages of web and native apps in groups. Consider the needs of:

1. Users
2. Businesses
3. Developers

Native App
==========

- Performant
- Network independent
- Installable
- Platform dependent

Web App
=======

- Less performant
- Online only

Web App
=======

- Responsive
- Discoverable
- Linkable
- Progressive
- Safe

PWA
===

- Installable
- Network independent
- Re-engageable

